# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/

# Firebase / FCM client config.
#
# `android/app/google-services.json` IS committed for the `tzmc-notifications`
# Firebase project — the contents are public client identifiers (Google
# explicitly designs google-services.json/firebaseConfig to ship inside
# clients; security is enforced server-side via Firebase Security Rules,
# SHA fingerprints and the FCM service-account key on the backend).
#
# iOS GoogleService-Info.plist is still provided at build time via the
# CI secret — drop it in locally only.
ios/Runner/GoogleService-Info.plist
.pub/
/build/

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
/android/app/debug
/android/app/profile
/android/app/release

# Generated files
*.g.dart
*.freezed.dart
